<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Legend Status — Dirty Bastard</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Oswald:wght@700&family=Barlow:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background:#E8E0D4;font-family:'Barlow',Arial,sans-serif;">

<!--[if !mso]><!-->
<div style="display:none;max-height:0;overflow:hidden;mso-hide:all;">20 cycles. You're in the 1%. Welcome to Legend status.&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;</div>
<!--<![endif]-->

<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="background:#E8E0D4;padding:48px 16px;">
  <tr>
    <td align="center">
      <table width="580" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="max-width:580px;width:100%;background:#F5EFE6;border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 8px 40px rgba(13,59,35,0.18);">

        <!-- GOLD TOP BAR -->
        <tr>
          <td style="background:linear-gradient(90deg,#B8860B,#DAA520,#B8860B);padding:12px 40px;text-align:center;">
            <span style="font-family:'Barlow',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:4px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#1A1000;">Legend Status — The Bastard Club</span>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <!-- HEADER -->
        <tr>
          <td style="background:#0A2415;padding:52px 40px 44px 40px;text-align:center;">
            <p style="margin:0 0 12px 0;font-family:'Barlow',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#DAA520;">{{ event.cycle_count }} Cycles Complete</p>
            <h1 style="margin:0;font-family:'Oswald','Impact','Arial Black',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:56px;font-weight:700;color:#F5EFE6;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:3px;line-height:1;">You're a<br>Legend.</h1>
            <p style="margin:16px 0 0 0;font-family:'Barlow',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:rgba(245,239,230,0.55);letter-spacing:1px;">That's not hyperbole. 20 cycles is rare.</p>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <!-- GOLD DIVIDER -->
        <tr>
          <td style="background:linear-gradient(90deg,#B8860B,#DAA520,#B8860B);height:3px;font-size:0;">&nbsp;</td>
        </tr>

        <!-- BODY -->
        <tr>
          <td style="padding:44px 40px 0 40px;">
            <p style="margin:0 0 16px 0;font-family:'Barlow',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:17px;font-weight:700;color:#0D3B23;line-height:1.5;">{% if person.first_name %}{{ person.first_name }}{% else %}You've{% endif %} — 20 cycles. Most guys don't make it to 5.</p>
            <p style="margin:0 0 16px 0;font-family:'Barlow',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#4A3C30;line-height:1.8;">You've been with us through the beginning. Before the product photos. Before the brand was what it's going to be. You were here, washing, cycle after cycle.</p>
            <p style="margin:0;font-family:'Barlow',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#4A3C30;line-height:1.8;">That matters to us. So we're not going to pretend this is just another milestone email.</p>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <!-- LEGEND BADGE -->
        <tr>
          <td style="padding:28px 40px 0 40px;">
            <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
              <tr>
                <td style="background:#0A2415;border-radius:4px;padding:32px;text-align:center;border:1px solid rgba(218,165,32,0.3);">
                  <p style="margin:0 0 8px 0;font-size:40px;line-height:1;">🏆</p>
                  <p style="margin:0 0 4px 0;font-family:'Barlow',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:10px;color:#DAA520;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:4px;font-weight:700;">Unlocked</p>
                  <p style="margin:0 0 8px 0;font-family:'Oswald','Impact','Arial Black',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:28px;font-weight:700;color:#F5EFE6;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:2px;">The Legend Pack</p>
                  <p style="margin:0;font-family:'Barlow',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:rgba(245,239,230,0.5);line-height:1.6;">Dirty Bastard tee + hat + a mystery gift we think you'll actually use. Reserved for the ones who made it to cycle 20.</p>
                </td>
              </tr>
            </table>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <!-- WHAT'S NEXT -->
        <tr>
          <td style="padding:28px 40px 0 40px;">
            <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
              <tr>
                <td style="background:#ffffff;border-radius:4px;padding:20px 24px;border-left:3px solid #DAA520;">
                  <p style="margin:0 0 8px 0;font-family:'Barlow',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C4733A;">What Happens Next</p>
                  <p style="margin:0;font-family:'Barlow',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#4A3C30;line-height:1.8;">You've hit every milestone. Your subscription continues — and so does your status. Legend members get early access to new scents, exclusive drops, and the occasional thank-you we don't announce publicly. Stay subscribed.</p>
                </td>
              </tr>
            </table>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <!-- CTA -->
        <tr>
          <td style="padding:36px 40px 0 40px;text-align:center;">
            <a href="https://getdirtybastard.com/pages/rewards?utm_source=klaviyo&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=post-legend&utm_content=cta" style="display:inline-block;background:#DAA520;color:#0A1A00;padding:18px 48px;border-radius:4px;text-decoration:none;font-family:'Barlow',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;">Claim Your Legend Pack →</a>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <!-- SIGN OFF -->
        <tr>
          <td style="padding:40px 40px 44px 40px;">
            <p style="margin:0;font-family:'Barlow',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#4A3C30;line-height:1.8;">With respect,<br><strong style="color:#0D3B23;">— Dirty Bastard</strong></p>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <!-- FOOTER -->
        <tr>
          <td style="background:#0A2415;padding:32px 40px;text-align:center;">
            <p style="margin:0 0 6px 0;font-family:'Barlow',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:rgba(245,239,230,0.45);">Questions? <a href="mailto:hello@getdirtybastard.com" style="color:#C4733A;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;">hello@getdirtybastard.com</a></p>
            <p style="margin:0 0 6px 0;font-family:'Barlow',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:11px;color:rgba(245,239,230,0.25);">Dirty Bastard Laundry Co. · <a href="https://getdirtybastard.com?utm_source=klaviyo&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=post-legend" style="color:rgba(245,239,230,0.25);text-decoration:none;">getdirtybastard.com</a></p>
            <p style="margin:0 0 16px 0;font-family:'Barlow',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:10px;color:rgba(245,239,230,0.18);">715 W Orient St · Tampa, FL</p>
            <p style="margin:0;font-family:'Barlow',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:10px;color:rgba(245,239,230,0.18);">You're receiving this because you give a sheet. <a href="{{ unsubscribe_url }}" style="color:rgba(245,239,230,0.18);text-decoration:underline;">Unsubscribe</a></p>
          </td>
        </tr>

      </table>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>

</body>
</html>
